msgid ""
msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "What's with this place?\r\nHow can a cat café not have any cats!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "W-We'll have them back soon, Ma'am.\r\nI promise..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "<font_kind=yakuza_italic>Soon</font_kind>!? Don't take me for a fool!\r\nI'm done with this dingy café for good!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "Can't say I blame her..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "A cat café with no cats...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "What am I gonna do...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "Hey."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "Hi<symbol=em_dash_with_outline>iiieee! I-I-Is this an extortion!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "Eh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "Please spare me... I don't have any money...\r\nI've been in the red because of this cat-less cat café..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "Hang on, I'm not tryin' to extort you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "Huh? Really? Oh...! Are you a customer!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "Welllcome! Please, please, this way!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "H-Hey...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "Geez, you're a terrible listener..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "Welcome, sir, to the Nyan Nyan Café!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "What is this place?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "I'm glad you asked, sir! The Nyan Nyan Café\r\nis a paradise for coffee and cat lovers alike!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "The combination of cute and caffeinated will\r\nleave you energized all day long. At least, it <font_kind=yakuza_italic>would</font_kind>..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "You certainly talk big, buddy...\r\nbut I don't see any cats."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "Look right this way, sir!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "That's our number one cat...\r\nBrittany-chan!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "Brittany-chan..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "Hey, Brittany-chan! Come here!\r\nWho's a good girl?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "Uh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "Man. This isn't your thing, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "I adore my feline friends, sir,\r\nbut I'm honestly bad with them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "Even though you're the manager of a cat café?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "Yes, sir. I adore my feline friends,\r\nbut <font_kind=yakuza_italic>they</font_kind> don't care for </font_kind>me very much."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "I'm okay with domesticated cats,\r\nbut other cats won't even look at me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "Hmm, that's pretty rough.\r\nSo, is that the only cat you have?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "Yes, sir. The others, they...\r\nThey all ran away."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "That's right. I had gathered a few\r\nadorable furballs for our grand opening..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "...but none of them respected me.\r\nWhen I wasn't looking, they all darted off."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "And so Brittany is the only one who's left..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "Yeah... Brittany-chan doesn't really like me\r\neither, though. She just failed to escape."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "I guess I just can't really hang\r\nin this cutthroat industry, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "I wouldn't say you're <font_kind=yakuza_italic>un</font_kind>qualified,\r\nbut you're not exactly qualified either."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "No use crying over spilt milk.\r\nYou should just buy more cats."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "I can't do that! I used all my savings on this place.\r\nMy wallet's run dry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "Besides, I already decided this café\r\nis gonna exclusively shelter strays."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "Why strays?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "Well, most cafés are devoted to high-pedigree breeds,\r\nso street walkers never get any love."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "I'm gonna set myself apart by bringing\r\nthe runts out into the spotlight!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "Naturally, any paw-pals we bring in will\r\nget a full grooming and special orientation."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "Huh... So it's a humanitarian thing, too.\r\nI've never heard of something like this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "But strays are super good at avoiding people.\r\nWhenever I approach 'em, they just scamper off."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "I wish I could find ones that would be okay\r\nwith spending their lives pleasing the public."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "Don't be ridiculous. That's not possible."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "What?\r\n...<font_kind=yakuza_italic>Me</font_kind>?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "I guess if I have to...\r\nThere, there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "Y-You're incredible, sir! Brittany-chan doesn't\r\nwarm up to <font_kind=yakuza_italic>anyone</font_kind> like this! This is amazing!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "Are you sure?\r\nShe seems pretty friendly to me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "I promise. Brittany-chan's never been\r\nlike this with any of my customers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "Maybe you have a hidden power, sir!\r\nThe power to befriend cats...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "Ah, that's it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "Um, if it's all right with you,\r\nI could really use some help."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "I... need you to gather stray cats for me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "Excuse me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "That's right. With my frankly lacking charm,\r\nit's impossible for me to round them up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "But you, you have the skills to get them\r\nused to spending time with people...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "And once they trust humankind, you'll scoop\r\nthem up for your café. That's it, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "Yeah! Isn't it a great idea!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "Ah! Don't leave!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "Pleeease! My life depends on this...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "I don't care. Why should I go through all that trouble?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "You should just give up on being a stray cat\r\nspecialist and borrow money to buy cats instead."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "But... stray cats are..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "Why do they have to be strays?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "I mean... don't you feel bad for them?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "It's not just Brittany-chan.\r\nAll cats deserve love."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "The high-pedigree ones, the dirty ones on the street...\r\nIt doesn't matter what breed they are."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "If there's a furry friend in need,\r\nI want to help them push onward."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "But strays get rounded up by animal control...\r\nand almost always get put to sleep."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "They're especially strict on that in Kamurocho.\r\nI can't let that continue."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||||4"
msgid "I want to save every last one."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||||4"
msgid "And I want people to see that strays are just\r\nas cute as regular cats once you wash 'em off."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||||4"
msgid "Hm..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||||4"
msgid "Hmmm..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "86||||4"
msgid "All right.\r\nI'll help, for a bit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||||4"
msgid "Y-You mean it, sir!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||||4"
msgid "Yeah, but I'm not doing this for you.\r\nThis is for the cats."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "89||||4"
msgid "I won't stand for them getting killed.\r\nNo animal deserves a fate that cruel."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||||4"
msgid "Thank you so much, sir!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||||4"
msgid "It's Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san! You're a real blessing to feline-kind!\r\nNow let's clean up the streets!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||||4"
msgid "So? What do you need me to do?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||||4"
msgid "Right. If you come across a stray somewhere,\r\ngive it food until it takes a shine to you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||||4"
msgid "It might take a few attempts before\r\nit really latches on, so just keep trying!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96||||4"
msgid "So I find cats, and feed them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "97||||4"
msgid "Yes. Each one will like different food, though.\r\nTake that into consideration."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "98||||4"
msgid "I'll go anywhere in the country for my feline friends!\r\nGive it your all, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||||4"
msgid "If things go well, I may even scrounge\r\ntogether a thank-you gift someday."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||||4"
msgid "Sounds good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||||4"
msgid "Well then, Kiryu-san...\r\nThe time is meow!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||||4"
msgid "(What have I gotten myself into...?)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||||4"
msgid "It's a crime to be that cute..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||||4"
msgid "That should be good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||||4"
msgid "Okay, time to get in touch with that café manager."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "106||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san! Thank you so much!\r\nI'll make sure this little guy loves his new home!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||||4"
msgid "Let me know if you find any more kitty cats!\r\nThanks in advance!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||||4"
msgid "That should be good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||||4"
msgid "Okay, time to get in touch with that café manager."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||||4"
msgid "It's Kiryu.\r\nI found a cat for you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||||4"
msgid "That's great news, Kiryu-san!\r\nWhere are you right now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112||||4"
msgid "Onomichi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||||4"
msgid "Onomichi...\r\nI don't think I recognize that street name."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "114||||4"
msgid "Well, it's down in Hiroshima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||||4"
msgid "Oh, yes yes. That one.\r\n...Wait, <font_kind=yakuza_italic>Hiroshima</font_kind>!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "116||||4"
msgid "What? I thought you said you'd go anywhere\r\nto help one of your feline friends."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "117||||4"
msgid "Th-That's true... but I didn't really think\r\nyou'd go so far away..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "118||||4"
msgid "Regardless, I'll keep my promise!\r\nJust wait there, I'll send someone!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "119||||4"
msgid "I'll make sure they're there soon.\r\nThanks again for this, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "120||||4"
msgid "Nyan Nyan Café, at your service!\r\nI heard you have a furry friend for us!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "121||||4"
msgid "Please let us know if you find any more!\r\nWell, I'm off!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "122||||4"
msgid "Well? That's a lot of cats.\r\nYou guys should be set now, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||||4"
msgid "Yes! We're chock full of furry friends.\r\nThank you so much for all your help!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||||4"
msgid "I know this isn't much...\r\nbut I want you to have it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||||4"
msgid "I guess this is the end of my journey.\r\nHonestly, I'm a little sad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||||4"
msgid "But all those adorable furballs you found\r\nwill be waiting for you at my café, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "127||||4"
msgid "Feel free to stop by whenever you want!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "128||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I will."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "129||||4"
msgid "Meow then... Thank you again!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "130||||4"
msgid "Hey, what's going on, you guys?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "131||||4"
msgid "Whoa! They haven't been this amped for a while!\r\nThey must've really missed you, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "132||||4"
msgid "Hm? Why do you say that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "133||||4"
msgid "Like I said, they've been pretty low-energy.\r\nI'm pretty sure it's 'cause they were lonely."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "134||||4"
msgid "Is that true, you guys?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "135||||4"
msgid "That reminds me, Kiryu-san! How would you\r\nfeel about coming in to feed them every so often?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||||4"
msgid "That way they won't miss you so much!\r\nI don't want 'em running out on me again..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||||4"
msgid "I'm not so sure."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "138||||4"
msgid "Hm..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||||4"
msgid "Hmmm..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "140||||4"
msgid "Guess I can't say no.\r\nI've come this far. Can't back out now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||||4"
msgid "Y-You really mean it!?\r\nYou're the cat's meow, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||||4"
msgid "Well, just come see me when you're available!\r\nLet's make these little guys purr!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||||4"
msgid "(I don't have any cat food...)"
msgstr ""

